ayers chain allows to map tNG-multilayers bands onto those of periodic bulk\nAT-graphite's at different $k_z$ values. We also obtain the Landau level\ndensity of states in the quantum Hall regime for magnetic fields of up to 50~T\nand confirm the presence of nearly flat bands around which we can develop\nsuppressed density of states gap regions by applying an electric field in N > 3\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jun 2022 14:24:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
